k; old packet_id |\n\n## Infrastructure Code Examined\n| File | Purpose | Finding |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| fanout-run.cjs | Fan-out dispatch + timeout | F-006 (4h cap), F-005 (default mismatch) |\n| fanout-pool.cjs | Stall watchdog + pool mgmt | F-016/R-1 (no observability alert) |\n| deep_review_auto.yaml | Review workflow | F-002 (3 ephemeral markers) |\n| deep_research_auto.yaml | Research workflow | F-002 (3 ephemeral markers) |\n\n## Files NOT in Prior Map (Net-New Discoveries)\n- `review/lineages/native/.deep-review.lock` (stale, dangerous)\n- `review/lineages/codex/iterations/iteration-{1-50}.md` (50 placeholder duplicates)\n- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/123-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/glm/review-report.md` (orphaned pre-migration)\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/glm/resource-map.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/glm/resource-map.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/glm/resource-map.md","time":{"start":1782885458691,"end":1782885458714}},"id":"prt_f1c4122df001hqnGwXUQSblQ8l","sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d86ffeWVTNwJkfGpd5iH","messageID":"msg_f1c40b934001XeXzDcHbCM2Atj"}}
